.H 2 "as"
This cookbook defines how to use the assembler.
.H 3 "recipes"
.VL 1i
.LI "%.o: %.s"
Construct object files from assembler source files.
.LE
.H 3 "variables"
.VL 1i
.LI as
The assembler command.
Not altered if already defined.
.LI as_flags
Options to pass the assembler command.
Not altered if already defined.
The default is empty.
.LI as_src
Assembler source files in the current directory.
.LI dot_src
Source files constructable in the current directory
(unioned with existing setting, if necessary).
.LI dot_obj
Object files constructable in the current directory
(unioned with existing setting, if necessary).
.LI dot_clean
Files which may be removed from the current directory in a clean target.
.LE
